r ~ 2--3 millimagnitude\nbiases, also meeting this requirement, but with more room for improvement. Our\nforward-model code has been released on Zenodo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2021 19:00:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 17:47:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-07"}
