ather than a quadriwave process, and proposing an alternative\nappellation, namely \"grating shadow phase microscopy\" or \"grating-assisted\nphase imaging\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2021 20:09:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2021 16:10:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Apr 2021 05:33:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 15 May 2021 04:54:34 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2022 17:11:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-15"}
